        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <p>Selling property in Spain involves complex legal procedures and tax obligations that require expert guidance to ensure a successful and compliant transaction. At <%= link_to "Roper Lawyers", "https://roperlawyers.com" %>, we are specialist Spanish property lawyers with over 14 years of experience helping British and Irish clients successfully sell their Spanish properties. Our English-speaking team provides comprehensive legal support throughout the selling process, ensuring maximum returns while meeting all legal and tax requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <%= render 'main_page_sections/reviews', locals: { reviews: @reviews } %>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="pb-4 m-3 text-center">Why You Need Legal Support When Selling Spanish Property</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <p>Selling property in Spain involves significant legal and tax implications that can affect your final proceeds. Spanish capital gains tax, non-resident tax obligations, and proper documentation requirements must all be handled correctly to avoid penalties and maximize your returns. Our expert lawyers ensure full compliance with Spanish law while protecting your interests throughout the sale process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <p>We handle all aspects of the legal sale process, from preparing necessary documentation and calculating tax obligations to negotiating contract terms and attending completion. Our comprehensive approach ensures your property sale is conducted efficiently, legally, and with maximum financial benefit to you as the seller.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-light">
    <div class="container px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="pb-4 m-3 text-center">Our Property Sale Services</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Pre-Sale Legal Preparation</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Comprehensive preparation including title verification, outstanding debt clearance, and ensuring all property documentation is in order for sale.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Tax Planning & Calculation</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Expert calculation of capital gains tax, non-resident tax obligations, and strategic advice to minimize tax liability on your property sale.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Contract Negotiation</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Professional review and negotiation of sale contracts, ensuring favorable terms and protecting your interests as the seller.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Documentation Management</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Preparation and management of all required legal documents, certificates, and declarations needed for a compliant property sale.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Completion Support</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Full support through completion including notary attendance, deed signing, and ensuring all legal requirements are met.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-12 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Post-Sale Tax Compliance</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Assistance with post-sale tax filings, capital gains declarations, and ensuring ongoing compliance with Spanish tax authorities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="pb-4 m-3 text-center">Spanish Property Sale Tax Obligations</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <h4>Capital Gains Tax</h4>
          <p>Non-resident sellers are subject to Spanish capital gains tax on property sales. We calculate your exact liability and advise on legitimate deductions to minimize your tax burden.</p>
          
          <h4>Non-Resident Tax</h4>
          <p>Special tax obligations apply to non-resident property sellers. We ensure full compliance with Spanish tax law and handle all necessary filings and payments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <h4>Withholding Tax</h4>
          <p>Buyers are required to withhold 3% of the purchase price for non-resident sellers. We manage this process and help you reclaim any overpayment after tax calculations.</p>
          
          <h4>Municipal Taxes</h4>
          <p>Local council taxes may apply to property sales. We handle all municipal tax obligations and ensure compliance with local requirements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-light">
    <div class="container px-4 py-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <h2 class="pb-4 m-3 text-center">The Spanish Property Selling Process</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <h4>1. Pre-Sale Preparation</h4>
          <p>We review your property documentation, clear any outstanding issues, and prepare all necessary certificates and declarations for sale.</p>
          
          <h4>2. Marketing Support</h4>
          <p>Legal advice on marketing your property, including compliance with advertising regulations and preparation of property information packs.</p>
          
          <h4>3. Offer Evaluation</h4>
          <p>Professional evaluation of purchase offers, including legal and financial implications of different terms and conditions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
          <h4>4. Contract Preparation</h4>
          <p>Preparation and negotiation of sale contracts, ensuring all terms protect your interests and maximize your returns.</p>
          
          <h4>5. Completion Management</h4>
          <p>Full management of the completion process, including notary coordination, final documentation, and fund transfers.</p>
          
          <h4>6. Post-Sale Compliance</h4>
          <p>Assistance with post-sale tax filings, capital gains declarations, and any ongoing legal obligations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

